> Hydras wento toward his quaters, he had several things to think but first he had to do several things. Hydras opened the com link to Scourge and Cyclonus and said "Scourge, Cyclonus... Report, what's the status of the base?"

"This is Cyclonus." the ex-minion's voice came over the link. "The
repairs to the base itself are nearly complete." Cyclonus paused for a
moment, Scourge's voice could be heard in the background, although his
words could not be made out clearly.

Cyclonus came back on the line, "However there has been a secondary
security breach. We are trying to lock it down."

Cyclonus' voice paused again, and then continued, "Someone was able to
breach our security protocols while we were engaged in locating the
Autobot and Maximal. I am sending Scourge around the base now to be
sure that we haven't missed anything."

"I haven't missed anything." Scourge's voice could be clearly heard in
the background now. "But I'm feeling kinda twitchy"

Cyclonus' voice continued, "Hydras, who or what ever it was that came
in after the Autobot did was extremely good."

(TAG)

Preston
